# Prisma
# NOTE: migration_lock.toml is intentionally NOT ignored. Prisma requires it to
# be committed — it records the datasource provider, guards against an
# accidental provider switch, and without it `prisma migrate diff
# --from-migrations` fails outright ("Could not determine the connector from the
# migrations directory"). It was previously ignored here in error.

